Package WHG

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Renderable
    This interface is used to draw the objects on the screen.
    Updateable
    This interface is used to update the objects on the screen mainly for the movement of them.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimatedBlock
    This class is an extension of block and implements the Renderable interface and is used to draw the blocks in the background that change color.
    Ball
    This class is used to draw and update the blue balls in the game.
    Block
    This abstract class is used for a basic block in the game, including balls, walls, coins, and the square.
    Coin
    This class is used to draw and update the yellow coins in the game.
    GameCompletedMenu
    This class is used to draw the menu that pops up once the game is completed.
    LevelFive
    This class is used to draw level five on the screen to be played.
    LevelFivePreMenu
    This class is used to draw the menu that pops up once level four is completed right before level five.
    LevelFour
    This class is used to draw level four on the screen to be played.
    LevelOne
    This class is used to draw level one on the screen to be played.
    LevelThree
    This class is used to draw level three on the screen to be played.
    LevelThreePreMenu
    This class is used to draw the menu that pops up once level two is completed right before level three.
    LevelTwo
    This class is used to draw level two on the screen to be played.
    MenuOne
    This class is used to draw the very first menu on the screen.
    MenuThree
    This class is used to draw the third menu on the screen.
    MenuTwo
    This class is used to draw the second menu on the screen.
    musicStuff
    This class is used to play the music and the sound effects of the game.
    Square
    This class is used to draw and update the red square in the game.
    TopBar
    This class is used to draw the black top bar at the top of the screen that displays the menu button, what level you are on, and the death count.
    Wall
    This class is used to draw the walls on the screen.
    WHGRunner
    This class is used to run The World's Hardest Game.
